item.title: About Me
item.description: figure { display: inline-block; margin: 0 auto; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; } figure img { vertical-align: top; border: 5px solid #ffffff; border-bottom: 50px solid #ffffff; } figure figcaption { font-size: 75%; text-align: left; margin-top: -40px; margin-left: 5px; } Hello!
